[SN]TITLE[SN]
Found: Lost teddy bear reunited with owner

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A four-year-old boy has been reunited with his lost teddy bear nearly a week after it went missing at an airport in the US.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
28 July 2017 Last updated at 08:36 BST
Luke, from Texas, lost his bear after his family's return flight from Colorado to Dallas.
But fortunately for Luke, his teddy bear was actually just on a little adventure...
Check out the video to see what it got up to!
